@startuml
title Sueca - Fluxo Atual (GraphQL + WebSocket)

actor "Jogador (Flutter UI)" as UI
participant "WebSocketService (frontend)" as WSF
boundary "GraphQL API (/graphql)" as GQL
control "LobbyService (in-memory)" as Lobby
boundary "WebSocket Handler (/ws)" as WSH
control "Hub" as Hub
control "RoomHub" as RH

== 1) Entrar com nickname ==
UI -> GQL : mutation createPlayer(nickname)
GQL -> Lobby : CreatePlayer(nickname)
alt nickname ja existe (case-insensitive)
  Lobby --> GQL : devolve player existente (idempotente)
else nickname novo
  Lobby --> GQL : cria player_N
end
GQL --> UI : playerId + nickname

== 2) Abrir lobby ==
UI -> WSF : connect(roomId="lobby", playerId)
WSF -> WSH : GET /ws?roomId=lobby&playerId=...
WSH -> Hub : AddClient("lobby", client)
Hub -> Hub : GetOrCreateRoom("lobby")
Hub -> RH : AddClient(client)
WSH --> WSF : websocket conectado

UI -> GQL : query rooms
GQL -> Lobby : ListRoomsDetailed()
Lobby --> GQL : rooms[]
GQL --> UI : rooms[]

== 3) Criar sala ==
UI -> GQL : mutation createRoom(input)
GQL -> Lobby : CreateRoom(name, hostId, maxPlayers, isPrivate, password)
alt sala privada sem password
  Lobby --> GQL : error password required
  GQL --> UI : erro
else pedido valido
  Lobby --> GQL : room criada (host entra logo)
  GQL --> UI : room
end

== 4) Entrar na sala ==
UI -> GQL : mutation joinRoom(roomId, playerId, password?)
GQL -> Lobby : JoinRoom(roomId, playerId, password)
alt password invalida/ausente em sala privada
  Lobby --> GQL : erro de password
  GQL --> UI : erro
else join valido
  Lobby --> GQL : room atualizada
  GQL --> UI : room
end

== 5) Entrar na sala de espera ==
UI -> WSF : connect(roomId=<roomId>, playerId)
WSF -> WSH : GET /ws?roomId=<roomId>&playerId=...
WSH -> Hub : AddClient(roomId, client)
Hub -> Hub : GetOrCreateRoom(roomId)
Hub -> RH : AddClient(client)

note right of Hub
RoomHub e criado de forma lazy:
so existe quando o primeiro cliente
WebSocket entra nessa sala.
end note

loop cada 2 segundos (polling no frontend)
  UI -> GQL : query room(id)
  GQL -> Lobby : GetRoom(id)
  Lobby --> GQL : estado da sala
  GQL --> UI : playersCount, players, host, status
end

note over UI,WSH
No estado atual, a sincronizacao da sala
de espera e feita por GraphQL polling.
WebSocket fica conectado, mas o lobby ainda
nao usa broadcast realtime ligado ao EventBus.
end note

== 6) Sair ou eliminar sala ==
alt jogador sai
  UI -> GQL : mutation leaveRoom(roomId, playerId)
  GQL -> Lobby : LeaveRoom(...)
  Lobby --> GQL : room atualizada
  GQL --> UI : ok
else host elimina
  UI -> GQL : mutation deleteRoom(roomId, requesterId)
  GQL -> Lobby : DeleteRoom(...)
  Lobby --> GQL : true
  GQL --> UI : ok
end

== 7) Fecho de websocket ==
WSF -> WSH : close socket
WSH -> Hub : RemoveClient(roomId, client)
Hub -> RH : RemoveClient(client)
alt RoomHub fica vazio
  Hub -> Hub : remove roomId do mapa
end

== 8) Quando chegam 4 jogadores ==
alt playersCount == 4
  UI -> UI : ativa botao "Ir para jogo"
  note right of UI
Hoje este botao navega para o ecra de jogo
no frontend. Ainda nao existe mutation
startGame ligada ao fluxo atual.
  end note
end

@enduml

